</PRE>
<H2>GL_PROXY_TEXTURE_2D are available only if the GL version  is  1.1</H2><PRE>

</PRE>
<H2>or     greater.     GL_TEXTURE_3D,    GL_PROXY_TEXTURE_3D,    and</H2><PRE>

</PRE>
